text: Hey Addison, I'm good thanks how are you? I'm currently in my final semester of studying VFX at the University of West London and hope to break into the industry this summer/fall. I'm mainly interested in compositing but my final project at Uni also involves a lot of matchmoving with 3DEqualizer.

I moved to London from Vienna(Austria) in 2016 to study VFX and hopefully find work here. In my spare time, I like to play/watch football or go skating. Can't think of anything else for my introduction hope that's enough :smile:
